<a href="/questions/1517598-do-you-have-his-art-on-abarat-in-all-the">Do you have his art on abarat in all the editions?or is it only available in specific editions?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1517598'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F768878.Abarat">like</a></span>

