        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer283035549" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4778546338544541595">Upon rereading this teenaged favorite, present me enjoyed this less. A lot of the mystery in this first book is revealed in the third, so knowing the secrets made this read less exciting. Remembering correctly, teenager-me loved guessing at who Candy would fall in love with, which has never been the point of this book, really, but that&apos;s where a lot of my past excitement came from. I have loved the sequel to this book more than this one in the past, so I&apos;m interested to see if that is still so!</span>
  <span id="freeText4778546338544541595" style="display:none">Upon rereading this teenaged favorite, present me enjoyed this less. A lot of the mystery in this first book is revealed in the third, so knowing the secrets made this read less exciting. Remembering correctly, teenager-me loved guessing at who Candy would fall in love with, which has never been the point of this book, really, but that's where a lot of my past excitement came from. I have loved the sequel to this book more than this one in the past, so I'm interested to see if that is still so!</span>
