              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5645967-laurel?shelf=how-to-make-memorable-characters">how-to-make-memorable-characters</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5645967-laurel?shelf=how-to-make-a-good-series">how-to-make-a-good-series</a>, 
