        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2242476830" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2598564426494066781">Oh Abarat <br/>Recommended to me by my Dad who is a HUGE Clive Barker fan<br/><br/>I read Weaveworld and I found that was very heavy going and the imagination was so vast. <br/><br/>I thought this would be the same<br/> <br/>Oh no no no. Pure and brilliant fantasy world that you can really sink your teeth into. So many adventures to be had and so much to see. I was fully immersed in this story and enjoyed the twists and turns along the way. <br/><br/>I am intrigued to see what happens with Candy in the next one</span>

